Dcode v1.0 Executor Commands

Variables

var:name=value          → Declare and assign variable
                        Example: var:x=10
Printing & Math

print:text              → Print text or variable values
print:root:value,n      → Calculate n-th root of value
print:exp:base,exponent → Calculate base^exponent
print:random:min,max    → Generate random integer between min and max
print:expression        → Evaluate math (+, -, *, /, ^)

Arduino (stubs)

arduino:compile         → Compile Arduino sketch
arduino:upload          → Upload Arduino sketch
arduino:serial:...      → Send serial command

Input

input:keyboard:KEY      → Check if key is pressed (A, B, C, SPACE, ENTER, ESC)
input:mouse             → Get mouse position

Networking

net:bluetooth:scan      → Scan Bluetooth devices
net:wifi:list           → List Wi-Fi networks

Utilities

console:clear           → Clear console output
console:log:msg         → Log message to console

